---
---

<section id="why-smolops" class="why-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="why-grid">
      <div class="why-content">
        <span class="section-label">Why SmolOps</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Built for people who run businesses, not computers.</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">
          We started SmolOps because we saw the same thing over and over: small business owners
          buried in manual processes, sold software they'd never learn, and too busy to care about
          either. There had to be a better way.
        </p>

        <div class="value-props">
          <div class="value-prop">
            <div class="value-icon">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#1c7237" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3>Zero learning curve</h3>
              <p>If you can send an email or a text, you can use SmolOps. We meet you where you are, not where tech companies wish you were.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="value-prop">
            <div class="value-icon">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#1c7237" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
                <polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3>Hours back in your week</h3>
              <p>The processes you dread &mdash; data entry, reordering, lead research &mdash; happen automatically while you're serving customers.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="value-prop">
            <div class="value-icon">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#1c7237" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M20 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H8a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/>
                <circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3>Personalized, not one-size-fits-all</h3>
              <p>We learn how your specific business works and tailor every automation to your workflows, vendors, and customers.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="value-prop">
            <div class="value-icon">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#1c7237" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="23"/>
                <path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3>Costs less than a part-time hire</h3>
              <p>Get the output of a back-office assistant at a fraction of the cost &mdash; without the overhead, training, or management.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="why-visual">
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-number">10+</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Hours saved per week on average</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-number">0</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Apps to download or dashboards to learn</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-number">24/7</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Your AI agents work around the clock</div>
        </div>
        <div class="quote-card">
          <p>"I just text a photo of my stockroom and get an order sheet back. It's like having the world's best assistant."</p>
          <span class="quote-attr">&mdash; What our clients say</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .why-section {
    background: var(--white);
  }

  .why-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 64px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .why-content .section-subtitle {
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .value-props {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 28px;
  }

  .value-prop {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .value-icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: rgba(28, 114, 55, 0.08);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .value-prop h3 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    color: var(--green-dark);
  }

  .value-prop p {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .why-visual {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .stat-card {
    background: var(--cream);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 28px 24px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .stat-number {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-size: 2.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--green-dark);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .quote-card {
    grid-column: 1 / -1;
    background: var(--green-dark);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 32px 28px;
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .quote-card p {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    opacity: 0.95;
  }

  .quote-attr {
    font-size: 13px;
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .why-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 48px;
    }
    .why-visual {
      max-width: 500px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .why-visual {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
